    "description": {
      "value": "<div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You have mastered techniques to take advantage of every drop in any enemy's guard, gaining the following benefits:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">When you hit a creature with an opportunity attack, the creature's speed becomes 0 for the rest of the turn.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Creatures provoke opportunity attacks from you even if they take the <a href=\"https://5e.tools/actions.html#disengage_phb\"  onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.pHandleLinkMouseOver(event, this, 'actions.html', 'PHB', 'disengage_phb', null)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseLeave(event, this)\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseMove(event, this)\"  ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\" >Disengage</a> action before leaving your reach.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When a creature within 5 feet of you makes an attack against a target other than you (and that target doesn't have this feat), you can use your reaction to make a melee weapon attack against the attacking creature.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t</div>",
